{"body": "I like the idea in general, but I don't like the invention of new DSL for such a tiny purpose.\r\n\r\nCan we reuse already invented DSL from Rack:\r\n\r\n`param(\"user[id]\")` should give you the value of the input with name `user[id]` in a web form.\r\n\r\nBenefits:\r\n\r\n* give people a clean vision how to obtain values of inputs from complicated form.\r\n* support edge cases like `param(\"user[projects_attributes][]\")`\r\n* reuse and improve existing code in Rack", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4385900", "created_at": "2012-03-08T07:04:54Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5311#issuecomment-4385900", "updated_at": "2012-03-08T07:04:54Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5311, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/bogdan", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/91913f6ab8085bab0f2aa43995ba8ca2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F926d19e70f74c20f796d376aafa3c6e2.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/received_events", "gravatar_id": "91913f6ab8085bab0f2aa43995ba8ca2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "bogdan", "type": "User", "id": 122436, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bogdan/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523ed0c3bd354364b9012fb0"}, "id": 4385900, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5311"}
